title: Independence for Catalonia? The 10 players Spain could lose - including Busquets, Fabregas & Pique!
description:
With debate again raging in Catalonia regarding a possible independence from Spain, we look at how this could affect the Spanish national team and who could star for a potential Catalonia side.

With outspoken Gerard Pique leading the line, we take a look at nine other Spanish national players who, if Catalona were to separate from Spain, would be lost to La Roja - and could play a part in a Catalan national side. 

Do you think a Catalan national team could qualify for the World Cup with players of this calibre?
